- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper deals with the properties of regular languages, which are often studied in the context of algorithms and data structures. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possibility as the paper deals with the complexity of regular languages and their properties.
